{"id":232689771,"title":"[精釀啤酒] Figueroa Mountain Brewing Co.","content":"版上似乎比較少看到有人分享精釀啤酒，希望能拋磚引玉一下，不知道有沒有也喜歡喝精釀的朋友？\n\n在台灣精釀啤酒風行過一陣子，但似乎沒有之前一樣的快速成長。幸好台灣有許多熱情的廠商，依舊不斷引進各種新酒。\n\n最近新嘗試的就是費革洛阿山脈 Figueroa Mountain Brewing Co.這間酒廠3款啤酒。首先是這款：\n\nHoppy Poppy IPA\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/yK8QaP3.jpg\n\n這是一款西岸風格的IPA，明顯的葡萄柚、柑橘類的香氣，帶有一點清新花香與松針，苦味柔和。\n\nLizard's Mouth Imperial IPA\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/Id3N9tw.jpg\n\nImperial IPA 比起普通來得更重，這支濃度有 9 %。具有比較熱帶水果的香氣，木瓜、芒果、百香果等，會是酒花愛好者的愛。\n\nDavy Brown Ale\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/YzjuvDc.jpg\n\n飽滿溫和的味道，焦糖麥芽、巧克力、一點點咖啡的感覺。酒體柔順帶有些許甜味，非常易飲，又帶有一點苦味收尾不至於過膩。\n\n順帶一提我是在 you & me 牛肉麵 Bar（本體是啤酒但牛肉麵也很好吃），和 Beer Rush Taproom（有 11 管超多生啤） 兩間店喝到的~","excerpt":"版上似乎比較少看到有人分享精釀啤酒，希望能拋磚引玉一下，不知道有沒有也喜歡喝精釀的朋友？在台灣精釀啤酒風行過一陣子，但似乎沒有之前一樣的快速成長。幸好台灣有許多熱情的廠商，依舊不斷引進各種新酒。最近新","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-15T08:01:20.847Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-15T08:01:59.301Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["啤酒","精釀啤酒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"酒肉穿腸過","department":"jui.f","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":11},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/yK8QaP3.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Id3N9tw.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/YzjuvDc.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"af65fe57-1d8d-4804-a69d-06ff7d49cd5b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yK8QaP3l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yK8QaP3l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yK8QaP3l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-15T08:01:20.847Z","updated